{
  "storyId": "agent-loop",
  "lang": "en",
  "voice": "mock:default",
  "builtAt": "2026-05-28T13:23:54.016Z",
  "totalMs": 69760,
  "steps": [
    {
      "stepIdx": 0,
      "lines": [
        {
          "idx": 0,
          "text": "At first glance, Claude Code looks like a coding chat box inside your terminal.",
          "durMs": 3920,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 1,
          "text": "You type a request, and it replies with an explanation.",
          "durMs": 2800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 2,
          "text": "But if it were only chat, it could not fix bugs, run tests, or edit code.",
          "durMs": 4480,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 3,
          "text": "Inside that box, it is observing, acting, and observing again.",
          "durMs": 2800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 4,
          "text": "That continuous work record is a Session.",
          "durMs": 1960,
          "gapMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "stepIdx": 1,
      "lines": [
        {
          "idx": 0,
          "text": "A Session is a continuous conversation inside a specific workspace.",
          "durMs": 2800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 1,
          "text": "A Turn is one request you send to Claude Code.",
          "durMs": 2800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 2,
          "text": "You might assume one Turn means one model call.",
          "durMs": 2520,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 3,
          "text": "But it is much more complex: Claude may need to think several times, inspect several things, and only then answer.",
          "durMs": 5600,
          "gapMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "stepIdx": 2,
      "lines": [
        {
          "idx": 0,
          "text": "让我们聚焦其中一个 Turn,看看里面到底发生了什么 —— 先从用户输入开始。",
          "durMs": 1120,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 1,
          "text": "Agent 开始准备上下文:先填入系统提示、记忆、规则、历史…",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 2,
          "text": "再填入这一轮真正要解决的问题。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 3,
          "text": "打包完成,发起第一次 LLM 调用。",
          "durMs": 840,
          "gapMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "stepIdx": 3,
      "lines": [
        {
          "idx": 0,
          "text": "极简单的任务,LLM 可能直接回答;但更多时候,它会决定先获取更多信息。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 1,
          "text": "于是 LLM 返回一个特殊结果:tool_use。",
          "durMs": 840,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 2,
          "text": "tool_use 不是答案,只是模型提出的一个动作请求。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 3,
          "text": "比如:读文件、搜代码、执行命令。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "stepIdx": 4,
      "lines": [
        {
          "idx": 0,
          "text": "接下来,Agent 真的去执行这个工具。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 1,
          "text": "执行完,工具返回 tool_result。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 2,
          "text": "关键在这:模型不是自己幻想文件内容。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 3,
          "text": "它拿到工具返回的真实结果,再继续推理。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 4,
          "text": "tool_use 是模型提出的动作;tool_result 是世界返回的证据。",
          "durMs": 840,
          "gapMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "stepIdx": 5,
      "lines": [
        {
          "idx": 0,
          "text": "现在把它们串起来 —— 这是这个 Turn 真实的调用链路。",
          "durMs": 1400,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 1,
          "text": "Call 产生 tool_use,Agent 执行得到 tool_result。",
          "durMs": 1400,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 2,
          "text": "tool_result 被塞回下一次 Call 的 context,上下文越滚越大。",
          "durMs": 1400,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 3,
          "text": "循环往复 —— 模型负责推理,工具负责行动,理解越来越完整。",
          "durMs": 840,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 4,
          "text": "直到某一次调用,模型判断信息已充分 —— 不再 tool_use,而是给出最终结论。",
          "durMs": 1120,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 5,
          "text": "从用户输入,到这最后一次 LLM 调用给出结果 —— 一个 Turn 就此终止。",
          "durMs": 1960,
          "gapMs": 300
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "stepIdx": 6,
      "lines": [
        {
          "idx": 0,
          "text": "Session —— 一次完整的会话。",
          "durMs": 840,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 1,
          "text": "Turn —— 一次用户请求,以及为回答它的全部工作。",
          "durMs": 840,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 2,
          "text": "LLM Call —— 一次带着具体 context 的模型请求。",
          "durMs": 1680,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 3,
          "text": "tool_use —— 模型想做什么。",
          "durMs": 840,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 4,
          "text": "tool_result —— 现实返回了什么 —— 指针又跳回 LLM Call,像一个 while 循环。",
          "durMs": 2520,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 5,
          "text": "出口只有一个 —— LLM 自行决策不再 tool_use,跳出循环、给出结论。",
          "durMs": 1400,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 6,
          "text": "把循环抽象出来,其实就是三个阶段:收集上下文 → 采取行动 → 验证结果。",
          "durMs": 1400,
          "gapMs": 300
        },
        {
          "idx": 7,
          "text": "而驱动它的只有两件事:模型负责推理,工具负责行动。",
          "durMs": 800,
          "gapMs": 300
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}